# CAPTCHA_Cracker

Implement convolutional neural network to extract the features from the CAPTCHA images.

Train the model with 640,000 images.

Highest achieved test acurracy: 98.7%.

Version information:
- python: 3.5.2
- Keras: 2.1.2
